snippet.title: EA SPORTS FC 26 | Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Innovation powered by you in every mode. The Club is Yours in FC 26, launching September 26. Pre-order now: http://x.ea.com/84657

Play your way with an overhauled gameplay experience, Manager Live Challenges that bring fresh storylines to the new season, and Archetypes inspired by greats of the game. http://x.ea.com/84762

Pre-order EA SPORTS FC 26™ Ultimate Edition by August 26 to receive:
An untradeable ICON Player Item at launch. 
Automatic upgrade to a Champion ICON later in the season.

EA SPORTS FC 25™ players will also receive:
An exclusive EVO that boosts any player’s shooting to 99.
Pick 1 of 5 untradeable ICON players rated 93+ from previous campaigns including Grassroot Greats, FUT Birthday, Dreamchasers & FUT Immortals in EA SPORTS FC™ 25. 

Pre-order EA SPORTS FC 26™ Ultimate Edition to receive:
Up to 7 days early access
6000 FC Points over 2 months (4500 FC Points over 2 months for Nintendo Switch)
Additional Football Ultimate Team™ Player Evolution Slot
Season 1 Premium Pass


Subscribe to see more from EA SPORTS FC™: http://bit.ly/pzw4VD

#EASPORTSFC #FC26

CROQUETAS CREMOSAS DE CALABACÍN Y ATÚN, fáciles y deliciosas. #LoliDomínguez #croquetas #calabacín #estilohida #hidaalimentacion #atún #receta #recetas #recetasfaciles #cocina #cocinafacil #comida #comidas

Ingredientes de las CROQUETAS CREMOSAS DE CALABACÍN Y ATÚN:
.
1 calabacín de 350g Aprox. (zucchini, zapallito, calabacita, Etc.)
1 cucharada de aceite
Sal (Cantidad al gusto)
100g Aprox. de cebolla caramelizada (Hecha en casa o comprada de buena calidad)
(Yo he usado cebolla caramelizada en conserva de Hida, lo puedes encontrar en su tienda online o en grandes superficies) https://www.hida.es/tienda/ 
En la tienda online de Hida tienes un 5% de descuento poniendo el código LOLI5
100g Aprox. de atún en aceite ya escurrido
Pan rallado para rebozar las croquetas
2 huevos
Abundante aceite para freír
.
.
Ingredientes de la salsa bechamel de las CROQUETAS CREMOSAS DE CALABACÍN Y ATÚN: 
.
20g de aceite de oliva (2 cucharadas) 
45g de mantequilla
65g (6+1/2 cucharadas) de harina de trigo común o de todo uso
750ml (3 tazas) de leche entera o semidesnatada
Nuez moscada rallada (Cantidad al gusto)
Pimienta recién molida (Cantidad al gusto)
Sal (Cantidad al gusto)
.
